<plot>An RKO "Streamliner" short featuring the south-of-the-border rhythms of the Luis(Luiz) Arcaraz orchestra. It opens with "La Virgen de la Macarena" featuring the brass section; Dolores Brown dances and Raul Martinez sings while the band plays "Be Careful" and ends with the band doing "Arcaraz Mamba."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?367462</url></doc>
